title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Attempt to export data from a table containing highlight/map. 3. Observe the thrown exception.
